name: Man Eats Fish
description:
Take your boat out onto the high seas to find and catch fish for your customers. Better quality fish means higher reviews for your shop, more customers, and more money!

Catch many kinds of fish, from boring and bland to exciting and delicious.
Upgrade your boat to explore further into the world and find bigger and better fish.
Can you turn your little fish & chip shop into the pride of the seafood world?
